copy of passport. The passport must be valid for at least 6 months
after the assumed expiration date of the Russian visa.

If the Italian students haven't bought air tickets yet, they should have 
to indicate in the form the extended period: September, 1-16 (regardless 
of the real flight dates).

We kindly ask your students to send this information before June, 4.
----------------

You find the form cited by Olga enclosed to this e-mail. 
Note that who has not the passport (or has a passport that does not 
satisfy the requirements written in the above message) has to apply as 
soon as possible in order to obtain it.
