Dear Carmine,

We try to obtain invitations with perpose "studing" for all
non-russian students. The University International department
preliminarily agreed with this.
In this case the students will not have to pay consulate taxes
regardless to their affiliations.
The rules  are common for all russian consulates including the ones in
Genova and Milano.

Olga

