Please, go in the International Relations office of your universities, and 
ask if there are offers of funds for studying travels (as usually 
happens here in Tor Vergata University).

If yes, then you can try to 
obtain such funds (with the help of your professors/advisors) to be 
helped in facing the expences of your participation at the Rome-Moscow 
school 2012.

If no, ask (in the same office) if your professors/advisors can ask the 
Rector of your universities to offer such funds.

Try!

Carmine Di Fiore

