The official date of the end of the school is September 30, even if 
lectures probably will end on Friday (Sept 28) as in the schools
of 2010 and 2011. In particular, I inform you that all not-italian
students and profs of the school leave on Sept 30 or October 1.
However, if you have decided or are deciding to leave from Tor Vergata on 
September 28, please take into account that at most in the early afternoon 
of September 28 there will be a final round 
table among the students and the professors of the school.
Try not to leave before such meeting.
Take also into account that 75 minutes are surely sufficient 
in order to succeed in catching a train in Rome Termini railway station, 
leaving from the Faculty of Science of Tor Vergata.


